_sText:
This is a remake of classic Aim_ak-colt_pool From CS 1.6 (http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/2243) for CS:S.

I tried to keep the design very basic and similar to the original one.

The current version is a Release Candidate, please give me all the feedback that u can so we can go to Final :)
